# AI & Voice — Agent Rules

**Read the full plan first:** `docs/AI_VOICE_PLAN.md`

## Role

Member 3 — AI & Voice. Build `POST /api/chat` + voice hooks. Do not build map UI or data layer.

## Allowed paths (edit only these)

- `services/ai/*`
- `app/api/chat/*`
- `features/voice/*`
- `hooks/useChat.ts`
- `lib/chat-types.ts`
- `scripts/test-intent.mjs`, `scripts/test-chat.mjs`

## Forbidden (never edit)

- `workers/`, `services/data/`, `services/experience/`, `services/routing/`
- `features/chat/`, `features/map/`, `app/page.tsx`
- `lib/intent-schema.ts`, `lib/types.ts` (read only)

## Backend integration

- Call Siddharth's API via HTTP: `POST ${API_URL}/api/spatial/query`
- Default `API_URL`: `http://localhost:8787`
- **Never** import from `services/data/*` or `spatial-engine`

## AI integration

- OpenRouter → Grok via `OPENROUTER_API_KEY`, `OPENROUTER_MODEL` in `.env.local`
- Default model: **`x-ai/grok-4.3`** — do not use retired `x-ai/grok-2-1212`
- Intent output must validate with `intentSchema` from `lib/intent-schema.ts`

## Multi-agent order

1. Contracts → 2. Intent → 3. Chat API → 4. Voice/client  
All on branch **`cursor/ai-voice-plan`** (PR #6). Commit + push after each agent passes exit checks.  
Use **one Cursor session** for full context. See `docs/AI_VOICE_PLAN.md`.

## Before finishing

```bash
git diff master --name-only   # must be only allowed paths
```

Run the exit checks for your agent number in `docs/AI_VOICE_PLAN.md`.
